title: Australian diary. No. 002
brief_description: This diary features Kauri timber in Western Australia, Sydney from the air - how it looks from four miles up, a motor yacht regatta, Kingaroy’s peanut industry, ‘Bernborough’ winning the Doomben race, and spring at Mt. Kosciusko. No credits available.
